      • add

        public boolean add​(E e)
        Overrides the boolean add(E e) method. If the list is empty the item is added automatically, subsequent items are compared to existing elements and if the existing element is greater than the new element, the new element is inserted into its position.
        Overrides:
        add in class java.util.ArrayList<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>
